<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/mathml/v3p0/schema/xsd/mathml3.xsd" identifier="lwai_a6d6c28c-8f4b-4f96-b5d5-f51f9f759703" title="L16 Reading Checkpoint — The Tell-Tale Heart" adaptive="true" time-dependent="false" xml:lang="en-US">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>C</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-item-body>
    <div data-catalog-idref="tts_passage">
      <blockquote>
        <p>TRUE! — nervous — very, very dreadfully nervous I had been and am; but why <em>will</em> you say that I am mad?</p>
        <p>— Edgar Allan Poe, "The Tell-Tale Heart" (1843)</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt data-catalog-idref="tts_prompt">
        <p>Read the passage above. Based only on this passage, the central conflict is —</p>
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="A">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_A">
          <p>external — the character against a locked gate blocking his escape</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_A" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_A">
              <p>Look again — no gate, door, or physical barrier appears anywhere in these lines.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="B">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_B">
          <p>external — the character against another person on the road</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_B" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_B">
              <p>He speaks to a "you," but no one in these lines acts against him or blocks his way. Listen for where the struggle actually lives.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="C">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_C">
          <p>internal — the character against his own fear and self-doubt</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_C" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-correct" data-catalog-idref="feedback_C">
              <p>Correct! Nothing in the world acts against him in these lines — the whole fight is the narrator against his own nerves and his desperate insistence that he is not mad. That's internal conflict.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="D">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_D">
          <p>there is no conflict; nothing happens in the passage</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_D" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_D">
              <p>Quiet doesn't mean conflict-free — listen to how hard he's fighting to convince you (and himself) that he isn't mad.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
